@node "System Requirements" "System Requirements"
                            System Requirements
                            ===================

`Mail2YAM' 1.8 requires:


* Amiga - the only and the one ^_-;
* OS2.1 or better
* RexxMast running

* rexxreqtools.library (from Aminet)
* rexxsupport.library

* YAM 1.3.3a            @{b}(ALREADY installed and assigned)@{ub}
* a text editor        (Ed, CygnusEd, GoldEd...)ą
* a WWW browser

* TCP device
  already mounted      @{b}(If you want to check if you've new mail)@{ub}



@{i}FOOTNOTES@{ui}

ą If you want to use your own editor you MUST know its arexx port name.
For example, CygnusEd's arexx port is named: @{b}rexx_ced@{ub}
@endnode

